Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.85,0:23:09.81,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:13.87,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}If Gordon, Grey, and Sekke\NWent to a Mixer Together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:13.87,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,If Gordon, Grey, and Sekke \NWent to a Mixer Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:13.87,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha! Bah-ha! Bah-ha-ha-haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:17.55,main,Helene,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:18.87,main,Erika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.14,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.96,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be at a mixer \Nwith people as cute as you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.13,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be my friend? You will? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.13,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:30.38,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Could we exchange contact info? \NI'll write you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.38,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:34.39,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.29,italics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.34,0:23:40.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:45.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove that even peasants \Ncan move up the ranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:49.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 29: "Path."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:55.00,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 29\N\N{\fs18}Path
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:53.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not giving up is my magic!
